=== 0.9.7 ===
2012-03-03  Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@canonical.com>

	* po/jockey.pot,
	* setup.py: [789] release 0.9.7

	* jockey/detection.py: [788] jockey/detection.py: Accept repository
	URLs with "file:/", too

