=== 0.9.6 ===
2011-12-08  Martin Pitt <martin.pitt@canonical.com>

	* po/jockey.pot,
	* setup.py: [769] release 0.9.6

	* jockey/oslib.py: [768] jockey/oslib.py: Use specified target_kernel
	for module aliases, too. Thanks Hedayat Vatankhah! (LP: #900851)

	* jockey/oslib.py: [767] jockey/oslib.py: Be robust against failure to
	open blacklist for writing. Thanks Hedayat Vatankhah! (LP: #900850)

	* gtk/autostart/jockey-gtk.desktop.in,
	* gtk/jockey-gtk.desktop.in,
	* kde/autostart/jockey-kde.desktop.in: [766] Fix some style issues in
	desktop files. Thanks Hedayat Vatankhah! (LP: #900819)

